item.title: About Me
item.description: I am a software developer. I’ve completed my engineering in Computer Science from Mumbai University, India. Currently working on several pet projects which can help me improve, I am open to opportunities, if you want to see my work please fill free to traverse around the website. If you want to contribute to projects, I work on please feel free to DM me in any of the following options or contact me page, or you can look at the source code yourself at my github repository.
